    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Whether you grow wings, lift yourself with currents of air, alter gravity, or through some other means related to your religion and domains, you can gain the power of flight temporarily. You gain the following benefits:</p><p><strong>Ability Score Increase.</strong> Increase your Dexterity or Constitution score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p><strong>Limited Flight.</strong> You can use an action to gain a Fly Speed equal to your Speed for 10 minutes. When the effect ends, you fall if nothing is holding you aloft. Once you use this feat, you can't do so again until you finish a Long Rest.</p>",
